Isora McNulty, Appellee, v. Lewis A. Reinert and Robert Clarke, Trading as the Alexandria Hotel, Appellants.Gen. No. 40,501.

(Abstract of Decision.)

Heard in second division, first district, this court at December term, 1938 ;opinion filed May 28, 1940.Andrew J. Farrell, for appellants; Henry Both, Charles O. Spencer and Richard M. Spencer, for appellee. Opinion by Justice Scanlan.

“Not to be published in full.”
